te. Your product will be safe at H-J and we can provide reports on product levels at your convenience.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"custom-packaging\">Customize Packaging</h2>\r\n<p>H-J can provide packaging, labeling, sorting, bar-coding, etc. according to your company needs. This value added service can offer flexibility in your supply chain.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"freight-services\">Freight Services</h2>\r\n<p>The H-J group of companies has more than 30 years of extensive experience in freight logistics. We have contacts and resources to handle any freight needs your company may have. We can offer competitive pricing and provide options for your needs.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"quality-control\">Quality Control</h2>\r\n<p>Our company can provide value added services such as the implementation of a quality control program to meet your specifications. You can guarantee the product will meet your quality standard before it leaves China. It will eliminate the chance to receive bad product in your country of destination.</p>\r\n</code>','Services','','publish','closed','closed','','services','','','2016-01-16 13:38:11','2016-01-16 08:08:11','',0,'http://127.0.0.1/wordpressTradeGlobal/?page_id=10',0,'page','',0),(11,1,'2015-12-11 06:29:48','2015-12-11 06:29:48','','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2015-12-11 06:29:48','2015-12-11 06:29:48','',10,'http://127.0.0.1/wordpressTradeGlobal/index.php/2015/12/11/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(12,1,'2015-12-11 06:30:37','2015-12-11 06:30:37','<ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\r\n  <li>Coffee\r\n      coffee2\r\n      coffee3</li>\r\n  <li>Tea\r\n      Tea2\r\n      Tea3</li>\r\n  <li>Coca Cola\r\n      Coca cola2\r\n      Coca cola3</li>\r\n</ul>','How We Work !!','','publish','closed','closed','','how-we-work','','','2016-01-10 10:51:05','2016-01-10 05:21:05','',0,'http://127.0.0.1/wordpressTradeGlobal/?page_id=12',0,'page','',0),(13,1,'2015-12-11 06:30:37','2015-12-11 06:30:37','','How We Work !!','','inherit